body.subject: Accommodation Contract - Majestic Mirage Punta Cana
body.message:
Dear LESLIE BURRIS,

We are pleased to confirm that your check-in at Majestic Mirage Punta Cana has been successfully completed.
Attached to this email, you will find the accommodation contract that you signed during the check-in process. This document outlines the terms of your stay at our hotel and the services available to you.
If you have any questions or need further assistance, please feel free to contact us by replying to this email or visiting the reception.
We hope you enjoy your stay with us.

Best regards, The Majestic Mirage Punta Cana Team
